182
00:08:13,219 --> 00:08:14,900
Yes, it’s very unfair for the US

183
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:17,210
to discriminate against Chinese companies.

184
00:08:17,210 --> 00:08:19,050
How could a country just outright ban

185
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:22,210
