market.

186
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:23,629
So unjust.

187
00:08:23,629 --> 00:08:26,990
And on a totally unrelated note, Google.

188
00:08:26,990 --> 00:08:29,110
One of numerous American tech companies

189
