195
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:47,430
open-source version of Android.

196
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:49,200
And that means Huawei is in trouble.

197
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:52,279
"Half of all of its shipments are sold outside
of China

198
