200
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,110
If they're not present on them,

201
00:08:58,110 --> 00:09:01,089
no matter how good anything Huawei comes up
with is,

202
00:09:01,089 --> 00:09:03,769
they're going to have a really hard time

203
00:09:03,769 --> 00:09:05,380
selling devices outside of China a

204
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:07,680
nd that is the essence of the problem."

205
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,240
One tech industry consultant said,

206
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:12,509
“It will be like an instant kill switch
for Huawei’s ambition

207
00:09:12,509 --> 00:09:14,660
to overtake Samsung in the global market.”

208
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:18,160
But Huawei has a little more time to figure
it out.

209
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,160
Because earlier this week,

210
